body: I was browsing manga to find something with good story... Well be carefull what you wish for
Holy shit this is a work of art.
Funfact: Page 51 "ฤดูร้อน" is Thai language, It mean summer. 😉

More people should read this. A "sexual" exploration of philosophy, psychology and sociology. I think it is trying to convey the depth and complexity of lust and sexual attraction and that it is inseparable from our way of life, art and the way our society and civilization functions. And it may be a huge mistake to repress explorations and analysis of sexual feelings and urges as they could have influence on many actions and decisions people make in their life which would affect society and the world as a whole

one of the best comics/manga i've ever read. so great to finally have it all wrapped up in a complete tank, with good scans and a great translation. it doesn't belong in this sad pit of incel fap fodder, but god bless [whoever] for posting it anway. made my damn day is what.
